Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.annotations

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.annotations
This package contains annotations used by this project.
  • Annotation Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    Deserialization
    Indicates that a constructor can be used for deserialization.
    Initializer
    This annotation is meant to be used on initialization methods to ensure NullAway understands that those methods are used to initialize variables.
    PersistentVariable
    Indicates that a field in an AbstractStructure subclass should be persistent.
